R7V/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 0 0 24px 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;市场总结&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;标准普尔 500 指数接近调整，战争仍看不到结束的迹象&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;由于担心局势升级，美国股市周一出现了大转变，加剧了抛售，引发了自 2022 年以来最长的单周下跌。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;当谈到美以与伊朗的战争带来的附带损害时&lt;/strong&gt;，欧洲正遭受越来越大的打击。最近，运载柴油前往非洲大陆的油轮突然改变了航线——就像飞涨的油价加剧了供应竞争一样。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;最近，四艘船在美国装载柴油型燃料并开始横渡大西洋。其中一架向直布罗陀发出信号，而另外三架则向阿姆斯特丹发出信号。然后他们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/vexdC8HuuyD9a40ARljIgMFPsbkdhyhV98FO_cSZ3zWFoDoblMu--GuGc9Vxd96ajanLDITttb7v-PauAuPVaXyhL3al_v4f-FHfsuVkyApgiT6xpBKESQY3rFuhDtoRuRKYdfCWKfRL6sEjhUamDPy3K6-aI3y3cfzxRvlD8nE90rDUUxWL6GELc9JiRsivo17R1yzUfPkEBv-be0arXWhc-u7R5qJeBT9Q7lM44zFHkyQuK2M1-1j5w_1A8PDfKc6rAfI0cg0Ig4dnIcDZ3tXr0Dcv4oppg8Ke2ZdhhOLOX7KHHXHiFDOLeRqQYkV5g_6tDF68dIv5QCWhHeQS9kxESlnuwLWFoGtVQSLVAeXujg3Jj0wfYhj_UOIWMgRXGfPFQKRxLGdUs-a9rHCiwpkcYXLflPXN1q4BInmU7DFbpTD_8a0pZy9o8uTVFTZm_22UlUnHsHNWQcHk8zopt75n3HN9cXZVuY4qdGroMec3ipCt3_hYXYRHijAjgzwzR9QsCCc/-kqH1j_lVrH4tOy8ZQUFgjXpiKtPyjAZ/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着油轮驶离，欧洲柴油供应压力加大"&gt;决定急转弯&lt;/a&gt;，其中一艘前往西非，其他则前往东南方。由于波斯湾市场失去了数百万桶石油，亚洲的燃料供应已经面临&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/59IfpdBzLtXQ-vwKrID9OrrOrtYUEkiuvCUg_FVB-UqiKO2nG83oQvYzkyXp-lvFQRupBhYBR0n0feLqiv3rtFh8Gaj55taiMWuyTbVTnZyThXrP3Ql8NikqVp1572JlIW_sVyvCLMSGqyqPLKuQlgdI0Y00Lxlwtc38v6l_6Zq-ylAZGgykaPW8STHZ45TpsRHUjkerDQu60F6u9HgnVydei--H2kifiWBy7h4PLx3djlrdgfBu5UIO4Cqy-mAIOHupOcKaHSqOs16MZa764HXzQFYCqSEigUjVonuAQl1wd8ft_VI_-A-FNES7wC0poXjWiFPFB6X0MmwoKIx21iBiOIWDVjWtP6pjSFMhOIhHB78IDep8kGKmhuTN-kYTJ5GoDLAKWgvVQc3hJ3GSw8Ncse0-AqNGpl-wPY-Mc1UsWeE57fV0eDMMRQ_a-nsJECpBEYTkAdzhadnsv6ibX6oupJ-iuFQV2yfS2tHeFVMC0TjFJvWh8j7SN_gRUjQ2NVcEEX6-a9K4Ow/hceWLeghW68qt_ttyryJlqV5VcHoo5lB/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争将亚洲推向全球能源危机的前线"&gt;严重压力&lt;/a&gt;，而石油交易商和分析师&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Cp7_6ngECnLQGbKqs5px5r-0TzmjpZVNsO75iIQHayc7c2RNiZXRLHYXkZKCL4lJqiUEOv-TOnUWY9_mCOn3sa1RRMgjEm1gPGVOsUr-wHfM5G1ZpwpLPGCaAHI_ylpKIdh6p_fqjvUBEGi_9X_3zv3iBN2EkLfERnG2dvr-qazBv0txR7JWcKXoSqTAghHIFFYgJQxkYvUsD0cVMqmmDKrstBliBqN6KFlQ9IhPYSHesnaGII0GQ_eoqLIvJLywCdpJ0-9J4kfy3RUUYp-REcoPIOrjLlFqKw7_CsNpABXDAZNxs7sY9hw-2IIKslGKBzExCk07bZYDZiTBOi4Y-7HzSp8VBi0bVJ3budXyvN3p9CqqZJcDZGhFwAyi5qD8bH6UCgDfYIPw-eTuI0TKTqw-GJpDkFAfm8O_DCiIqP4X9oLVE0SnQLdZmD4I_w-yN1dxqxF5gq3TTsFYvA/NoorsZ9iyO7tkm2PoJHVe0LRSU-cFOHD/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="霍尔木兹海峡石油危机正在向西蔓延"&gt;表示，&lt;/a&gt;欧洲可能很快就会面临短缺。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/yT7v2l--AxFLDXohxjpP70NEDMp_Zi02hYotRhfk87iygJ7mlwTy8tNWqp8ZUarlMpm8zia1fPamNFs0O0xiMHN9xX9wC7IhTaIFAKlrkSwnksYc3VK1P_UfLjo5w0Kh6z-TqubRoE3-ANHSN_vmMaaEXjeodGC0POmSnm_VI5cwkQdy2bm3mMeUSh-ejslVocXHqKEIcijudWrfynjzWWqHawfOl9NSl2C6NbSRJpk39pDWRwa6dcwweVwhSUvyYrf0pN8AizFPd_0rYuKwPb9ttIsx9k3S4bcHVQxXIhCSNEwg6Q_OADxnBcVsNOFdyFTjDIfOeFObr64E24rQ-uempwxtQ5-JE4ZsJebT8e2MdknMw8z9oTD38xe2-8-fk5gZ7FoJ-EiGb-nJe27dvSZSWA/lD8ljVf8yEdzJnJkpFmyXBeCiYPeZ8